Entries.default: "You're telling me they don't get to shoot him or anything? I want my money back."
"An excellent first act. The ending felt rushed."
"Was that supposed to be a comedy?"
Pallegina groans and puts her face in her hands. You've heard this type of groan from her before, but only when she was in intense physical pain.
"Our temple plays aren't half so entertaining. Let's watch it again."
